text.div: • Include codes from http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActRelationshipType where concept is-a EBE

name: ActRelationshipEndsBeforeEnd
title: ActRelationshipEndsBeforeEnd
description: The source Act ends after the end of the target Act (i.e. if we say "ActOne EBE ActTwo", it means that ActOne ends before the end of ActTwo, therefore ActOne is the source and ActTwo is the target).
